          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The composition of the C-14 target has",
                "been measured using the ERDA method(Elastic Recoil",
                "Detection Analysis) to determine absolute layer",
                "thicknesses.The following values have been obtained.",
                "See Sample."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "C-14 thickness 384-mug/cm**2, C-12 thickness",
                " 50-mug/cm**2, C-13 less or equal 1-mug/cm**2 thick,",
                "O-16 thickness 8-mug/cm**2, other constituents(Z=11-30)",
                "approximately 8-mug/cm**2. Contributions in the",
                "spectrum from the O-16 content were negligibly small.",
                "The significant C-12 content of the C-14 target",
                "required the measurement of a spectrum of the",
                "C-12(C-12,C-9) reaction on a separate C-12 target,",
                "thickness 200-mug/cm**2 for background subtraction."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Q3D magnetic spectrograph at Hahn-Meitner-",
                " Institute."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The reaction products were identified using the",
                " energy loss(delta-E) of the particles in the",
                " gas-filled focal-plane detector, the energy signal(E)",
                " from the scintillator behind it and the time of flight",
                " of the particles through the spectrograph."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*EN-RSL*.An overall energy resolution of 220 keV was",
                "obtained for the C-12 target and 250 keV for the",
                "C-14 target due to its larger thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
